		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="397" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">歌裴莉娅和科培琉司依次进行一次划击，均造成<span color="#bfffdf">对应元素</span><span>的</span><span color="#edffbf">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司牵着歌裴莉娅一同旋转2周，造成5段<span color="#7fffd7">30%</span><span>伤害，随后停下。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="426" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">送走歌裴莉娅后，科培琉司立即展开<span textDecoration="underline">寒芒冰嶂</span><span>，该护盾为歌裴莉娅和科培琉司共用，同时开始暴露</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffe599">芒性核心</span><span>直至组曲结束；随后便等待歌裴莉娅回归。<br/>再次施放时刷新护盾量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="1014" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司与歌裴莉娅开始进行表演，主角为科培琉司，场地内形成静止的3个霜之心，其不断产生冰爆造成<span color="#99ffff">60%</span><span>伤害，其可被歌裴莉娅的风刃触发扩散，额外造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>该技能分三个阶段：送别，独奏，回归，持续3个</span><span textDecoration="underline">循环</span><span>、8/3个</span><span textDecoration="underline">回合</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/冰风组曲%B7科培琉司的劫罚.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
